Setup ---


sudo apt-get install build-essential cmake
sudo apt-get install libgtk-3-dev
sudo apt-get install libboost-all-dev
sudo apt install python3-virtualenv
sudo apt-get install python3-tk
virtualenv venv
./venv/bin/pip install opencv-python
./venv/bin/pip install opencv-contrib-python
./venv/bin/pip install playsound
# ./venv/bin/pip install matplotlib
# ./venv/bin/pip install numpy
# ./venv/bin/pip install scipy
# ./venv/bin/pip install scikit-image
# ./venv/bin/pip install dlib

Testing setup ----
./venv/bin/python
# import dlib
import cv2

Download raw.githubusercontent.com_opencv_opencv_master_data_haarcascades_haarcascade_frontalface_alt2.xml
and put it in haarcascade_frontalface_alt2.xml

Download https://github.com/kurnianggoro/GSOC2017/raw/master/data/lbfmodel.yaml
and put it in lbfmodel.yaml

Boo laugh sound from http://soundfxcenter.com/video-games/super-mario-64/8d82b5_SM64_Boo_Laugh_Sound_Effect.mp3

Running ----
./venv/bin/python boo_game.py